53
0:03:03.16,000 --> 0:03:07,000
Botswana -- upper middle-income country in southern Africa,

54
0:03:07.16,000 --> 0:03:1,000
democratic government, good economy,

55
0:03:10.16,000 --> 0:03:12,000
and this is what happened there.

56
0:03:12.16,000 --> 0:03:14,000
They started low, they skyrocketed,

57
0:03:14.16,000 --> 0:03:17,000
they peaked up there in 2003,

58
0:03:17.16,000 --> 0:03:19,000
and now they are down.

59
0:03:19.16,000 --> 0:03:21,000
But they are falling only slowly,

60
0:03:21.16,000 --> 0:03:23,000
because in Botswana, with good economy and governance,

61
0:03:23.16,000 --> 0:03:26,000
they can manage to treat people.

62
0:03:26.16,000 --> 0:03:29,000
