the same rate as United States.

93
0:04:54.16,000 --> 0:04:56,000
And you'll find Madagascar,

94
0:04:56.16,000 --> 0:04:58,000
and you'll find a lot of African countries

95
0:04:58.16,000 --> 0:05:01,000
about as low as the rest of the world.

96
0:05:01.16,000 --> 0:05:05,000
It's this terrible simplification that there's one Africa

97
0:05:05.16,000 --> 0:05:07,000
and things go on in one way in Africa.

98
0:05:07.16,000 --> 0:05:09,000
We have to stop that.

99
0:05:09.16,000 --> 0:05:12,000
It's not respectful, and it's not very clever

100
0:05:12.16,000 --> 0:05:14,000
to think that way.

101
0:05:14.16,000 --> 0:05:18,000
(Applause)

102
0:05:18.16,000 --> 0:05:21,000
